responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F50866A249F0CA9B60557C940BFF2AB6", "Here I rest, a master of cursed quill, yet to offer my greatest of ills. The instrument of my demise can be yours if you dare to desire. Press upon my greatest children in proper order to defile.")
